h2 Your App's Design

h3 Help us to understand your visual design preferences. Upload any existing design elements that are relevant to your app.

form
  fieldset
    input#project-design-file(type="text", ng-model="vm.filename")

    button.add-design-file(ng-click="vm.add()") +

  ul.added-design-files
    li(ng-repeat="filename in vm.imageFilenames")
      .label {{filename}}

      button.remove(ng-click="vm.imageFilenames.splice($index, 1)") x

  button.submit(type="submit", ng-click="vm.next()") Next
